# Web Vulnerability Scanner

A modular, educational web vulnerability scanner built step-by-step
to understand web security concepts and scanner architecture.

This project evolves version by version to demonstrate how a real
security tool grows from a simple scanner into a structured engine.

---

# Project Structure

current/
    Active development version

versions/
    v1.0 – Basic modular scanner
    v2.0 – Multi-page crawler
    v3.0 – Form-aware injection engine
    v4.0 – Boolean-based blind SQL detection (Latest)

