# Report File

After scanning completes, results are saved to:

current/report.txt

The report includes:
- Per-page findings
- Severity classification
- Summary statistics

---

# Severity Levels

HIGH   → Confirmed vulnerability  
MEDIUM → Blind/behavior-based suspicion  
LOW    → Misconfiguration or weak security  
INFO   → Informational output  
OK     → No issue detected  
ERROR  → Scan execution error  

